message.content: cs.AI, cs.COGSCI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SY - The paper discusses machine consciousness and machine intelligence, which are both topics related to artificial intelligence (AI). The paper also mentions the ill-defined notions of cognition and intelligence, which falls under cognitive science (COGSCI). The proposed remedies for improving the current state-of-the-art also involve machine learning (LG), neural networks (NE), and systems and control (SY).
